# 15. Advantages of the System

* Helps students understand their internship readiness
* Provides fast predictions
* Reduces unnecessary applications
* Encourages skill improvement

---

# 16. Limitations

* Uses synthetic dataset
* Does not include company specific criteria
* Real world factors like interviews not considered

---

